name: Attack Over Oz - Jet Fighter Battle Run Edition
name_original: Attack Over Oz - Jet Fighter Battle Run Edition
description:
Jet Fighters at the ready - Your City needs you!

Your secret flight ops mission is to protect the central Metropolis from enemy forces threatening to take control of the City.
In an evening raid, enemy supplies have been dropped for the advance of their ground troops.

Lead the battle flight against enemy jets and helicopters in this futuristic air battle of the skies, destroy their aircraft, intercept and capture their supplies, you must stop them reaching ground zero!

Upgrade your fighter jet and save the City from total enemy rule.
